Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Located in the heart of Penrith CBD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE has the pleasure of offering 12 -18 Castlereagh St, Penrith to the market, for sale via an Expressions of Interest campaign. 

Located in the heart of Penrith, with development potential for shop top housing. The property is located across the road from Penrith RSL and within close distance to education facilities, Penrith Westfield and Train Station. 

The key attributes of the asset include:

- Total site area of 2,673sqm* 
- FSR: 3:1/HOB: 24m 
- Located in the heart of Penrith
- Across the road from Penrith RSL
- Close to proposed Badgery’s Creek Airport
- Development potential for shop top housing
- Ideal location and access
- Gross income $230,390 (CPI inc)

The property will be sold via expressions of interest which will be closed on Thursday 22 March  2018. The vendor welcomes all offers between now and that date. 

For further details please contact the below listed agents; 

Peter Vines - 0449 857 100

Alex Mirzaian - 0400 523 523

Lord Darkoh - 0434 675 724

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Industrial, Pub, Hotel, Fast Food, Fuel

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive listing agent is pleased to present 1 Renshaw Street, Penrith; an exciting development opportunity within the rapidly growing Nepean region. 1 Renshaw Street boasts a significant 1.49Ha* raw land offering with developable IN2 Light Industrial zoning.  Commanding a prominent location, the property is just moments from Penrith CBD and Stockland’s new housing development, Waterside Estate.

With IN2 Light Industrial zoning, 12m height limit and flat topography, this site is ideal for development. These planning controls, along with the sites proximity to the busy Andrews Road, allows for the development of a variety of uses.

The site will also benefit from stable growth in the Penrith City Council which is due to rapidly expand with many new government backed developments occurring in the Greater Sydney region including; North-South Rail Link, Outer Sydney Orbital, & the Western Sydney International Airport. 

1 Renshaw Street, Penrith benefits from the following key attributes:
•Generous 14,892sqm* land offering
•IN2 Light Industrial zoning allowing for development upside (STCA)
•Potential uses include: Hotel/Motel Accommodation, Service Stations, Take Away Food & Drink, Childcare, Community Facilities, Function Centre, Self Storage and Warehouse & Distribution 
•Located in the heart of the rapidly growing Nepean region, just moments from Waterside Estate
•Close proximity to amenities, including upgraded Nepean Hospital, upcoming North-South rail line and future Western Sydney Airport

1 Renshaw Street, Penrith will be sold via an Expression of Interest campaign, closing 15 June 2021 at 4pm. 

For more information or to request access to the due diligence room, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

*Approx.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:

The site will be sold by way of Public Auction on Wednesday 26th August at 10.30am. For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents.
